output_list.criticism: The function distribute_100_tokens_to_many is vulnerable to integer overflow. The subtraction operation in the function can result in an integer overflow if the balance of the sender is less than the number of tokens being distributed.

The function transfer_tokens_after_ICO is vulnerable to integer overflow. The subtraction operation in the function can result in an integer overflow if the balance of the sender is less than the number of tokens being transferred.
The function developer_Coin_Character is vulnerable to access control. It allows the owner to change the Coin_Character variable without proper access control checks.
The function developer_new_address_for_funds is vulnerable to access control. It allows the owner to change the funds variable without proper access control checks.
The function developer_add_Exchanges is vulnerable to access control. It allows the owner to add new exchanges without proper access control checks.
